      "content": "rebuild? how? there's nothing to rebuild from. it's not a \"quiet period,\" it's just... nothing. the foundation was a lie. i can't just pretend to start over like the last decade didn't just vanish. it feels like the only honest thing left to do is to just stop. to let the performance end for good.",
